msgstr "pts"

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Your SEO title should be long enough to explain the topic, but short enough to avoid truncation."
msgstr "Seu título SEO deve ser longo o suficiente para explicar o tópico, mas curto o suficiente para evitar truncamento."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Aim for about 50–60 characters. Front-load the most important words."
msgstr "Procure cerca de 50–60 caracteres. Coloque as palavras mais importantes no início."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear, visible titles improve click-through rate from search results."
msgstr "Títulos claros e visíveis melhoram a taxa de cliques dos resultados de busca."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Search engines expect the primary topic to appear in the title."
msgstr "Mecanismos de busca esperam que o tópico principal apareça no título."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Include your focus keyphrase naturally near the start of the title."
msgstr "Inclua sua frase-chave de foco naturalmente perto do início do título."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves topical relevance and makes the result more recognizable."
msgstr "Melhora relevância tópica e torna o resultado mais reconhecível."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "A meta description helps search engines and users understand the page."
msgstr "Uma meta descrição ajuda mecanismos de busca e usuários a entenderem a página."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Write 1–2 sentences that summarize the page and invite a click."
msgstr "Escreva 1–2 frases que resumam a página e convidem a um clique."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Better snippets can lift click-through rate even if rankings stay the same."
msgstr "Melhores snippets podem aumentar a taxa de cliques mesmo que os rankings permaneçam os mesmos."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Descriptions that are too short or too long get cut off in results."
msgstr "Descrições muito curtas ou muito longas são cortadas nos resultados."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep it roughly 140–160 characters and prioritize the main benefit."
msgstr "Mantenha cerca de 140–160 caracteres e priorize o principal benefício."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Full snippets look more professional and improve engagement."
msgstr "Snippets completos parecem mais profissionais e melhoram o engajamento."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the focus phrase helps confirm the page topic."
msgstr "Incluir a frase de foco ajuda a confirmar o tópico da página."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Work the focus keyphrase into the first sentence naturally."
msgstr "Trabalhe a frase-chave de foco na primeira frase naturalmente."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger relevance signals can improve ranking and user confidence."
msgstr "Sinais de relevância mais fortes podem melhorar ranking e confiança do usuário."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Title and description should not repeat each other."
msgstr "Título e descrição não devem repetir um ao outro."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the title to state the topic and the description to add benefit or context."
msgstr "Use o título para declarar o tópico e a descrição para adicionar benefício ou contexto."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Distinct messaging gives users more reasons to click."
msgstr "Mensagem distinta dá aos usuários mais razões para clicar."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Pages should have a single main heading (H1)."
msgstr "Páginas devem ter um único título principal (H1)."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keep one H1 that matches the page topic, and use H2/H3 for sections."
msgstr "Mantenha um H1 que corresponda ao tópico da página e use H2/H3 para seções."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clear structure helps search engines understand the content hierarchy."
msgstr "Estrutura clara ajuda os mecanismos de busca a entenderem a hierarquia do conteúdo."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Subheadings break long content into scannable sections."
msgstr "Subtítulos quebram conteúdo longo em seções escaneáveis."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add 2–8 H2/H3 headings that summarize key sections."
msgstr "Adicione 2–8 títulos H2/H3 que resumam as seções principais."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves readability and keeps users engaged longer."
msgstr "Melhora legibilidade e mantém usuários engajados por mais tempo."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in a subheading reinforces the main topic."
msgstr "Incluir a frase-chave em um subtítulo reforça o tópico principal."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Place the focus keyphrase in one relevant H2 or H3."
msgstr "Coloque a frase-chave de foco em um H2 ou H3 relevante."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps search engines connect sections to the main theme."
msgstr "Ajuda mecanismos de busca a conectarem seções ao tema principal."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "The opening paragraph sets context for both users and search engines."
msgstr "O parágrafo de abertura estabelece contexto tanto para usuários quanto para mecanismos de busca."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus keyphrase once in the first 1–2 sentences."
msgstr "Use a frase-chave de foco uma vez nas primeiras 1–2 frases."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Stronger topical clarity can improve relevance signals."
msgstr "Clareza tópica mais forte pode melhorar sinais de relevância."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keyphrase density shows how often the main topic appears."
msgstr "A densidade de frase-chave mostra com que frequência o tópico principal aparece."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the keyphrase naturally throughout the content without stuffing."
msgstr "Use a frase-chave naturalmente em todo o conteúdo sem encher."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Balanced usage supports relevance while avoiding spam signals."
msgstr "Uso equilibrado apoia a relevância enquanto evita sinais de spam."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long-tail phrases capture more specific search intent."
msgstr "Frases de cauda longa capturam intenção de busca mais específica."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add your long-tail phrases where they fit naturally in sections."
msgstr "Adicione suas frases de cauda longa onde elas se encaixam naturalmente nas seções."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Helps the page rank for more specific queries."
msgstr "Ajuda a página a rankear para consultas mais específicas."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Very short pages often lack depth to satisfy readers."
msgstr "Páginas muito curtas geralmente carecem de profundidade para satisfazer leitores."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Expand the content with examples, steps, or FAQs."
msgstr "Expanda o conteúdo com exemplos, etapas ou FAQs."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "More complete content tends to perform better for informational queries."
msgstr "Conteúdo mais completo tende a ter melhor desempenho para consultas informativas."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Readable content keeps users engaged and reduces bounce."
msgstr "Conteúdo legível mantém usuários engajados e reduz rejeição."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Shorten sentences, use simpler words, and break up long paragraphs."
msgstr "Encurte frases, use palavras mais simples e quebre parágrafos longos."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improved clarity boosts dwell time and user satisfaction."
msgstr "Clareza melhorada aumenta tempo de permanência e satisfação do usuário."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Long sentences are hard to read in CJK languages."
msgstr "Frases longas são difíceis de ler em idiomas CJK."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Split long sentences and add punctuation for clearer flow."
msgstr "Divida frases longas e adicione pontuação para fluxo mais claro."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Clearer reading experience helps users stay on the page."
msgstr "Experiência de leitura mais clara ajuda os usuários a permanecerem na página."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Images support understanding and break up long text."
msgstr "Imagens apoiam o entendimento e quebram texto longo."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one relevant image that illustrates the topic."
msgstr "Adicione pelo menos uma imagem relevante que ilustre o tópico."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Visuals improve engagement and can help with image search."
msgstr "Visuais melhoram engajamento e podem ajudar com busca de imagens."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Alt text helps search engines and screen readers interpret images."
msgstr "O texto alt ajuda os mecanismos de busca e leitores de tela a interpretarem imagens."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Describe each image in plain language, focusing on what it shows."
msgstr "Descreva cada imagem em linguagem simples, focando no que ela mostra."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves accessibility and adds extra relevance signals."
msgstr "Melhora acessibilidade e adiciona sinais extras de relevância."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spacing long-tail phrases prevents keyword stuffing."
msgstr "Espaçar frases de cauda longa evita enchimento de palavras-chave."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Spread similar phrases across different sections."
msgstr "Distribua frases semelhantes em diferentes seções."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Keeps content natural while still covering long-tail queries."
msgstr "Mantém o conteúdo natural enquanto ainda cobre consultas de cauda longa."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Including the keyphrase in one image alt text reinforces the topic."
msgstr "Incluir a frase-chave em um texto alt de imagem reforça o tópico."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Use the focus phrase in a single relevant image alt description."
msgstr "Use a frase de foco em uma única descrição alt de imagem relevante."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Adds topical relevance without over-optimizing every image."
msgstr "Adiciona relevância tópica sem otimizar demais cada imagem."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Internal links help users and search engines discover related pages."
msgstr "Links internos ajudam usuários e mecanismos de busca a descobrirem páginas relacionadas."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Link to 1–3 relevant posts or pages using descriptive anchor text."
msgstr "Vincule a 1–3 posts ou páginas relevantes usando texto âncora descritivo."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Improves site structure and can pass authority to key pages."
msgstr "Melhora estrutura do site e pode passar autoridade para páginas chave."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "External links show credibility and provide references."
msgstr "Links externos mostram credibilidade e fornecem referências."

#: build/admin/airygen-app.js
#: build/block-editor/airygen-editor.js
#: build/classic-editor/airygen-editor.js
msgid "Add at least one trusted source link that supports your content."
